 "name": "RPlog_Orson_the_Technician",
 "title": "Orson the Technician",
 "summary": "In the cleared area before the main house at Karrde's base on Myrkr, the mechanic Orson is in his element, absorbed in the intricate technical work that defines him. Methodical and lightning-fast, whistling tunelessly as he works, he reads machinery with the ease of long mastery while his mind turns over recent visions and the group's next steps. The log showcases Orson's formidable skill as a technician and the thoughtful, restless intelligence beneath his rough exterior.",
